Title: Calder Code 4 45deg lead slate 4" (1)
Description: Designed to provide a weatherproof seal around pipe penetrations, this Calder 4" 45° lead weathering slate is suitable for use on tile or slate roofs. Highly reliable, this slate is made of Code 4 lead, and is supplied with a 450mm base and a 150mm rear upstand.

Title: Calder Code 4 0-30deg uncut flexislate 450mm 25-125mm (1)
Description: Offering easy installation, Calder 25 - 125mm uncut 0 - 30D Flexislate is a robust pipe sleeving made up of a 450mm Code 4 lead base and a bonded EPDM synthetic rubber sleeve. Highly reliable, Flexislate is used to create a weatherproof seal around pipes, roof-mounted aerials or similar fittings that require penetration through your slate, tile or built-up felt roofing.
